<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT1.2">
<l>kaḷḷik kavaṭṭiṭaik kālai nīṭṭik kaṭaikkoḷḷi vāṅki macittu maiyai</l>
<l>viḷḷa veḻuti veṭuve ṭeṉṉa nakku veruṇṭu vilaṅku pārttut</l>
<l>tuḷḷic cuṭalaic cuṭupi ṇattīc cuṭṭiṭa muṟṟuñ cuḷintu pūḻti</l>
<l>yaḷḷi yavikkaniṉ ṟāṭu meṅka ḷappa ṉiṭantiru vālaṅ kāṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place where our father dances constantly, while, extending [her] leg into a fork of Euphorbia,</l>
<l>dragging a firebrand from the rim, mashing [it], clearly drawing the black, laughing boisterously,</l>
<l>being frightened, peering out athwart, frisking, being angry when the pyre with corpses</l>
<l>to be burnt is put to burn, she scoops up the dust [and] put it out, is Tiruvalaṅkāṭu.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
